In this article, President Donald J. Trump emphasizes the importance of achieving American energy dominance. He states that he has taken action in his first five months in office to remove unnecessary obstacles that would have hindered the United States from achieving this goal. The article also highlights the significance of the energy industry to the economy and future economic growth. It mentions that despite previous beliefs about declining energy resources, innovation and new technology have unlocked trillions of dollars' worth of energy for development. President Trump is committed to fulfilling his promises to the American people in this regard.